--Pred Base/Megatron/Switchblade--

The Pred Base's damaged sensors pick up Pegatron's advance, and 
quickly alert Megatron in the Control room. "Waspinator, you want 
something to do... well, DESTROY THE INTRUDER."

He opens a commlink again, "Perceptor, Nemesis Enforcer, enemy 
detected, get your cans out there and help Waspinator."

Switchblade taps his fingers on the wall, "Megs?"

Megatron's eyes glow, showing his irritating at being attacked, by 
apparently one target, as he turns to face Switcblade. "Swi--" He Is 
cut off by Switchblade, "Uhh, I've just remembered that I have 
something to err do... yah."

He backs out of the room, and heads down to the old engine room.
